programme.title: World Watch: Africa’s Hunter Ep14
programme.desc: Ikuti kehidupan pemangsa hebat di Zambia seperti singa, harimau bintang dan hyena, yang bersaing dalam dunia liar yang semakin mencabar. Pelbagai perubahan berlaku dari kelahiran impala serentak hingga kemunculan makhluk ganjil seperti anai-anai terbang. Alam liar Lembah ini bersedia menghadapi musim baharu. Episod kali ini mengenai anak singa Milo yang dilahirkan dalam klan yang kuat di Lembah Luangwa tetapi dia ditolak oleh ibu bapanya. Milo perlu berjuang sendiri untuk membuktikan dia boleh bersaing.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: 3S Serba Serbi Servis Ep5
programme.desc: Drama sitkom ini memaparkan perjalanan syarikat 3 S (Serba Serbi Servis) milik Datuk J yang menyediakan perkhidmatan penyelenggaraan di sebuah pangsapuri. Pelbagai telatah lucu dan aksi spontan berlaku dalam urusan seharian mereka dengan para penduduk di pangsapuri tersebut. Episod kali ini mengisahkan kesukaran yang dialami seorang gadis OKU bernama Fiena. Pak Daud dan pasukan Serba Serbi Servis telah mengambil inisiatif untuk cuba membantu menyelesaikan masalah Fiena yang ingin melanjutkan pelajaran ke universiti.

programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang memaparkan informasi berkenaan 24 jenis panyakit yang terdiri daripada penyakit berjangkit dan tidak berjangkit. programme.title: Citra: Luka Di Hati Diya Ep11
programme.desc: Kisah Diya Mirza, wanita penuh trauma yang hidup dalam ketakutan dan sering dibuli. Kehadiran Remmy, staf baharu yang naif namun jujur, membuka pintu hati Diya yang sekian lama tertutup. Namun, kisah silam kembali menghantui bila ayah tiri Diya muncul semula. Dalam pelarian dan pengorbanan, cinta mereka diuji. Mampukah mereka bertahan atau hati akan terus dilukai?. Remy masih sedih setelah kehilangan ibunya. Kehadiran Natrah telah mengganggu kehidupan Remy. Pelakon: Isyariana, Niezam Zaidi, Fauzi Nawawi, Lisdawati, Sherry Ibrahim, Fikhree Bakar, Kodi Rasheed, Lia Natalia, Azlan Komeng, Kak Girl, Syed Mirfan, Nonny Nadirah, dan Sanjna Suri.

programme.title: Galaksi Ep5
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Setiap episod mengandungi 3 segmen iaitu Tajuk Utama, Tahukah Anda (membawa trivia dan fakta menarik) dan Eksperimen (yang boleh dilakukan di rumah). Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim, membawa penonton meneroka dunia Ilmu Falak, bidang yang mengkaji pergerakan objek-objek samawi seperti matahari, bulan, dan buruj, serta peranan Jabatan Falak di Jabatan Mufti Negeri. Dalam segmen Tahukah Anda, penonton akan mempelajari tafsiran perkataan "falak" dalam al-Quran. Segmen Eksperimen pula mengajar cara menghasilkan Rubu Mujayyab D.I.Y. untuk mengukur kedudukan matahari.

programme.title: Spektra: Derhaka Cinta Jebat Ep20
programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. Bijaknya Jebat mengatur rancangan agar Aisyah jatuh cinta padanya hingga membawa kepada sebuah perkahwinan dengan niat ingin membalas dendam. Aisyah Humaira, suatu ketika dahulu pernah menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan adik lelaki Jebat, iaitu Tuah Iskandar. Tanpa usul periksa Jebat menjatuhkan hukuman tanpa memberi peluang kepada Aisyah untuk menjelaskan segala-galanya. Aisyah dituduh berlaku curang dengan Tuah dan menjadi penyebab musibah yang menimpa adik lelaki kesayangannya. Aishah sudah mula hilang kepercayaan terhadap Jebat disebabkan Kamelia. Jebat pula merancang sesuatu untuk membalas dendam! Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Azlee Khairi, Ikmal Amry, Mimi Ernida, Nina Fazurina, Wilma Muhammad dan Aznah Hamid.

programme.title: Simfoni Alam
programme.desc: Dokumentari memaparkan isu hidupan liar dan alam semulajadi. Taman Negara di Jerantut Pahang, merupakan destinasi menarik yang menjadi tarikan pelancong domestik dan antarabangsa menerusi bidang eko pelancongan berasaskan alam sekitar dan budaya tempatan. Juga, usaha Jabatan Perhilitan dalam memastikan Taman Negara terus dipelihara dari sebarang kerosakan agar ianya dapat terus dinikmati oleh generasi akan datang.

programme.title: KLTV 2025 Ep31
programme.desc: Sebuah rancangan informasi yang memfokuskan tentang dunia hiburan di Malaysia dari pelancaran music & wayang terbaru, isu isu panas terkini dan juga rancanga/Siri best untuk dilayan.

programme.title: Celebs Day Off S5 Ep02
programme.desc: Dihoskan oleh Asmawi, anda juga akan mengenali lebih lanjut kisah kehidupan dan karier tetamu undangan episod kali ini, Mekyun.

programme.title: Ekspresi Fesyen S4 Ep08
programme.desc: Aliya Marissa selaku pengacara berbual fesyen bersama pemilik jenama Cazaluna Accessories dan dalam GRWM ( Get Ready With Me) bergaya bersama tetamu jemputan, Mohsein Kushairi, seorang penyanyi dan akhiri bersama stylist terkenal, Min Luna dan ikuti perjalanan kerjaya beliau.

programme.title: Setulus Takdir Fattah Amira: Ijab Kabul Ep02
programme.desc: Sepertimana yang telah ditentukan Ilahi, segenap rasa kini bersatu dengan setulus takdir, dalam kemeriahan dan keindahan majlis ijabkabul penuh kasih serta restu, dibawakan secara langsung untuk tatapan kita semua.

programme.title: Budak Pendamping
programme.desc: Ia mengisahkan tentang seorang budak yang berumur 16 tahun, bernama Firash. Dibesarkan sebagai seorang anak tunggal di sebuah keluarga yang sentiasa sibuk dengan kerjaya, membuatkan Firash lebih senang bersendiriaan. Disebabkan itu keluarganya membuat keputusan untuk hantarnya ke sebuah kem. Disana Firash bertembung dengan Idlan dan rakannya Khai dan Sahar, serta sebahagian dalam Ahli Majlis Tertinggi Asrama (AMTA) bagi kem tersebut. Akibat ketidakpuasan mereka terhadap Firash yang kelihatan lembik, badannya menjadi tempat untuk mereka lepaskan kekerasan. Namun kehadiran budak pendamping mengubah segalanya untuk Firash tetapi ia juga menggugat kesejahteraan yang dah lama tidak bergelora. Lantas, adakah perjanjian antara Firash dan pendampingnya merupakan ilusi semata - mata ataupun terdapat hutang yang akan dituntut antaranya dengan Tuan Daud?

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga EP1 Ep1
programme.desc: Rodi bergaduh dengan pelanggan di Chow Kit selepas menipu dalam permainan jalanan. Pulang ke rumah, dia mendapati ibunya mahu melacur semula kerana terdesak wang. Rodi menyerahkan semua duitnya dan menolak tawaran kerja membunuh. Sementara itu, Kasyorga keluar bersama Hamdi ke rumah terbengkalai sebagai kenangan terakhir sebelum Hamdi berpindah.

programme.title: Pintu Neraka
programme.desc: Kisah ini mengisahkan tentang Kamasani, seorang tokoh perniagaan yang menghidap kanser tahap akhir, yang mencari Mahabub, seorang pertapa misteri yang dikhabarkan memiliki penawar. Selepas menjalani rawatan yang mahal, Kamasani merasakan penyakitnya semakin berkurang, namun dia mula mengalami kesan sampingan yang serius; dia berhalusinasi dan menjadi ganas. Titik perubahan berlaku apabila Vida, seorang wartawan televisyen, membongkar konspirasi ghaib Mahabub yang melibatkan nama-nama besar. Kamasani akhirnya sedar bahawa ramai yang telah menderita atau mati akibat keengganannya menerima takdir sendiri, lalu bertekad untuk membetulkan segalanya.

programme.title: Accident Man
programme.desc: Mike Fallon "Accident Man", adalah pembunuh dingin, dia adalah yang terbaik dalam apa yang dia lakukan. Tetapi apabila orang yang disayangi diseret ke dunia bawah tanah London dan dibunuh oleh krewnya sendiri, Fallon terpaksa merobek kehidupan yang dia tahu untuk membalas dendam kepada orang yang sebenarnya bermakna kepadanya.

programme.title: Black S2 EP6 Ep6
programme.desc: Black berdepan dengan kes yang paling menggentarkan apabila emosinya terganggu buat pertama kali - seluruh skuad keluar mencari Bagas, yang juga dikenali sebagai Lelaki Berparut Cangkuk yang telah menahan dua orang tebusan, yang nampaknya cedera. Borhan bersemuka dengan Rahman tentang kaitannya dengan penipuan insurans yang ada hubungan dengan Lelaki Berparut Cangkuk. Akhirnya, pertembungan yang tegang dikhuatiri akan meragut nyawa orang yang tidak bersalah.

programme.title: Transporter 3
programme.desc: Frank Martin terpaksa menghantar Valentina, anak perempuan pegawai kerajaan Ukraine yang diculik, dari Marseilles ke Odessa melalui Laut Hitam. Dalam perjalanan, dia terpaksa bersemuka dengan samseng yang ingin menggagalkan penghantaran tersebut

programme.title: Jangan Pandang Belakang Congkak
programme.desc: Tiga Sekawan tiba ke rumah datuk mereka, selepas mendapat surat jemputan. Mereka diberi syarat untuk tinggal selama tiga malam tanpa menyentuh apa-apa barangterutama congkak tua. Malangnya, selepas mereka membongkong congkak itu, kejadian pelik dan lucu berlaku, bulu ayam di mulut Johan, dan poket Asmat tiba-tiba penuh duit.

programme.desc: Reza berurusan dengan lelaki misteri dalam hutan untuk membeli sesuatu dalam guni - yang rupa-rupanya masih hidup. Di bandar, pelacur overdose meninggal dan bayinya diselamatkan oleh gelandangan, Pak Bakar. Kasyorga, bayi itu, hilang, dan Rodi nekad mencarinya. Sementara itu, Reza dan Datuk Zaza terlibat dalam konspirasi penculikan kanak-kanak melalui sindiket Rajoo. Di sebalik imej nelayan, Rajoo menjalankan operasi pemerdagangan manusia. Dalam subplot, Madam Kwan curiga dengan suaminya, Uncle Lim, selepas menemui bahan mencurigakan dan berakhir dengan tragedi - dibunuh oleh suaminya sendiri apabila cuba mendedahkankebenaran.

Namun apabila salah seorang daripada mereka terdedah kepada mereka, rasa curiga dan paranoia mula menjangkiti kumpulan itu, membawa ancaman yang lebih membahayakan daripada serangan di luar.

programme.title: Rasukan Ablasa
programme.desc: Kisah ini mengisahkan tentang kejahatan yang terbentuk sejak dahulu mengenai Omar yang menyembah syaitan demi mendapatkan ketaatan isterinya, Laila. Namun, penyembahan itu hanya membuatkan isterinya berlaku curang. Pada suatu hari, Omar terserempak Laila sedang berasmara dengan seorang lelaki bernama PB. Dalam keadaan marah yang amat sangat, Omar telah memenggal kepala Laila dan juga PB.

programme.title: Taxi 4
programme.desc: Tidak bernasib baik, kikir, tetapi menawan, detektif PD Marseille milien Coutant-Kerbalec mesti membantu komisioner Gibert yang lebih teruk daripada Clouseau menjaga penjenayah Belgium yang terkenal sebagai bahaya sama seperti - dan ditawan seperti Hannibal Lector. Kawan sejuk milien, pemandu teksi Daniel Morales, pada mulanya hanya bersetuju untuk menjaga anak-anak lelaki kawan mereka, kerana isteri milien, Petra, sedang menjalankan misi rahsia. Tetapi tidak lama kemudian, penjenayah Belgium itu melarikan diri, dan semasa mengejarnya, rakan-rakan itu tersandung pada satu perampokan bank dan sebuah vila megah milik raja dadah, di mana babak akhir yang hebat berlaku.

programme.title: Kelibat
programme.desc: Kisah ini mengisahkan sebuah keluarga yang berpindah ke rumah baharu dan diganggu oleh satu entiti ghaib misteri yang dikenali sebagai Kelibat. Gangguan Kelibat bukan sahaja berlaku secara fizikal, malah turut menghantui mereka dari segi emosi dan rohani.

programme.title: Wok EP3 Ep3
programme.desc: Deris tidak diterima kehadirannya oleh masyarakat sekeliling. Banyak yang memandang serong dan melayani dia begitu teruk sekali. Sehinggakan dirinya dipukul dan dihalau. Pertemuan dengan si anak dara dua, penjual bunga di pasar iaitu jirannya sendiri suria menjadikan deris ada juga yang prihatin.

programme.title: Anita Dunia Ajaib
programme.desc: Rumahtangga Amir dan Asmah berubah setelah mereka didatangi seorang pembantu rumah misteri yang membantu mendapatkan mereka cahaya mata. Selepas melahirkan anak dalam tempoh yang singkat, satu demi satu insiden aneh menimpa ahli keluarga dan kenalan mereka.

programme.title: Leftenan Adnan
programme.desc: Adnan memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang tentera dalam pasukan Askar Melayu setelah dikunjungi anggota tentera British yang datang ke kampungnya untuk merekrut lebih ramai anak tempatan. Tidak direstui keluarga, Adnan nekad untuk mengikuti latihan ketenteraan di Port Dickson. Perjuangan Leftenan Adnan dalam mempertahankan Tanah Melayu memberikan inspirasi kepada ramai anak muda tempatan.

programme.title: Penyamun Tarbus
programme.desc: Tuan Said seorang yang kaya raya tetapi sering mengelat dari membayar cukai, menyimpan semua rekod di dalam peti besi miliknya. Malang sekali, rekod dan tarbus miliknya dicuri penyamun - untuk membalas dendam terhadap Tuan Said kerana tidak menerima mereka bekerja atas faktor umur. Tidak ingin rahsianya diketahui, diupahnya penyiasat penyendirian untuk menjejaki penyamun itu.

programme.title: Pemburu Bayang
programme.desc: Zamri merupakan seorang bekas banduan yang ingin memulakan hidup baru bersama keluarganya. Namun, nasib tidak menyebelahinya apabila dia diburu kumpulan yang diketuai Ramon. Adik Zamri, Awie ialah seorang penyanyi kumpulan rock popular yang sedang menjalinkan hubungan cinta bersama Ella, yang juga penyanyi rock. Sesuatu terjadi yang menyebabkan Awie dan Ella putus hubungan. Manakala, Zamri pula diuji dengan pelbagai dugaan apabila isterinya dibunuh dengan kejam.

programme.title: Bintang Malam
programme.desc: Selepas dua belas tahun berlayar, Yazid dan Johari akhirnya pulang semula ke tanah air. Yazid pulang ke kampung manakala Johari pergi ke Kuala Lumpur dan bertemu Haslinda, Shima dan Aida. Bersimpati dengan nasib Haslinda, Johari ingin membantunya. Yazid pula keluar mencari Aisah di bandar - tetapi berdepan dengan pelbagai konflik dan tragedi.

programme.title: Matinya Seorang Patriot
programme.desc: Pengerusi Melati Holdings, Haji Saaban meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba yang menimbulkan keraguan tentang kematiannya. Safuan mengesyaki bahawa kematian bapanya ada kena mengena dengan syarikat bapanya. Saiful yang pada mulanya ingin membalas dendam kematian bapanya mula berubah apabila jatuh cinta dengan anak kepada ahli lembaga pengarah. Safuan menganggap Saiful telah mengkhianati keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Ragam Pemandu
programme.desc: Pemandu yang setia dan tidak pernah mengeluh, Hamid tidak disukai oleh isteri tuannya, Rubiah. Tuannya, Rahim pula seorang yang baik hati dan sukakan Hamid. Dia sering membantu membiayai pelajaran anak-anak Hamid dan menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi olehnya. Satu pertengkaran menyebabkan Hamid berhenti kerja namun Rahim tampil membantu mengambilnya bekerja di syarikat insurans miliknya.

programme.title: Aku Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Seorang petani dan anggota sukarelawan, Hamid dan Jaafar ingin menjatuhkan Jamali - wakil rakyat yang tidak telus dan kejam. Mereka berdua berusaha mendapatkan sokongan orang kampung supaya dapat menaikkan Hamid sebagai wakil rakyat baharu sekaligus menggantikan Jamali. Dharma dan Rosnah turut terpalit dengan kisah percintaan. Orang-orang kampung juga disarankan untuk menyimpan di Amanah Saham Nasional buat masa hadapan mereka di dalam kisah ini.

programme.title: Ringgit Kasorrga
programme.desc: Kekayaan, kemewahan dan hawa nafsu - semuanya boleh didapati di Pulau Kasorrga. Pulau khas buat warga elit ini menjadi tempat buat orang kaya untuk mencari ketenangan dan kepuasan. Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Dia Ibuku
programme.desc: Rohani perlu bekerja keras untuk menyara anak-anaknya, Jamal dan Jamil kerana statusnya sebagai seorang janda. Tanah terpaksa digadai untuk membiayai pelajaran Jamal di luar negara, itulah kesanggupan Rohani demi anaknya. Jamal pun pulang membawa keluarga bakal isterinya selepas pulang ke tanah air. Perjumpaan itu membawa kembali kenangan silam yang pahit.

programme.title: Anita Dunia Ajaib

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan Ep5174
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: Prosecutor, The
programme.desc: Based on a true case, young Ma Jia Jie pleads guilty to drug trafficking in exchange for a lighter sentence, as coerced by his defense lawyer. Huo Zi Hao, a former cop turned prosecutor, believes in his innocence and launches an investigation. Risking his life and career, Huo is determined to uncover the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Cape No. 7
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer tries to deliver seven old love letters attentioned to a Tomoko. As he falls in love with a young Japanese model also named Tomoko, he unravels their serendipitous connection.

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixs (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Three bizarre tales intertwine in this horror satire set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other's parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents' first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: Grandmaster, The
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tians daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: Stand Up Story
programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: The Monkey King 3
programme.desc: Monkey King, Pigsy and Sandy escort Monk Tang to retrieve the scriptures and accidentally head into the mysterious Female Kingdom. The Queen falls in love with Monk Tang at first sight, but her advisor orders Monk Tang and his disciples to be executed. As the four attract the appearance of River Spirit, the Female Kingdom is plunged into crisis!

programme.title: Everything is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met. When Pan discovers that his daughter is being abused by Hua, he vows to save her but eventually fall into their trap

programme.title: Bullet and Brain
programme.desc: Nine years ago, two legendary criminals, Bullet and Brain, vowed not to kill and lie before they disappeared. Both now return for a mission - to protect the granddaughter of the triad boss. Can they succeed without breaking their vows?

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 97
programme.desc: Mr Lo has three sons, Leung, Fay and Kung; and a daughter-in-law, Eliza. While they seem like a normal family, their relationships need mending. Leung and Fay play a prank on their brother Kung on his birthday by falsely claiming that he has won the lottery. This sets off a chain reaction of funny mishaps that finally brings the family together.

programme.title: The Last Dance
programme.desc: Amid the recession caused by the pandemic, debt-ridden wedding planner, Sheng, finds a lifeline as he transitions into a funeral planner. His unconventional approach leads to unexpected success, and his attitude toward his career and life is transformed after being inspired by the respected Master Wen.

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: High Forces
programme.desc: On its maiden flight, an A380 airliner is hijacked by armed gunmen. Among the passengers is international security expert Gao Hao Jun, whose daughter has been taken hostage, putting her life in grave danger. Determined to save her, Gao confronts the hijackers head-on. Can he rescue all the passengers and thwart the crisis?

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Shanghai
programme.desc: Ma Yong Zhen moves to Shanghai in the hope of becoming rich but ends up having to use his kung fu skills to survive and take revenge against the gang who killed his brother.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult: Ultimate Malevolence
programme.desc: The final chapter of 'Tales From The Occult', the movie features three short stories about two high school friends, a magician undergoing hypnosis to find her missing friend, and a man finding his way out of a mysterious building. The stories reveal the most terrifying and ugly side of human nature, where life and death are just a thought away!

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: Maoshan Heavenly Master
programme.desc: Prisoner Chi flees away under Master Zhangs custody, causing the latter to be expelled from his clan. On his way to find Chi, Master Zhang arrives at a place where many people vanish for no reason. He soon discovers that it is Chi who captures them in his training to become a serpent demon. The war between human and demon has just begun!

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: The Flag Of Iron
programme.desc: When super director Chang Cheh found new talent and blood with "The Five Venoms" actors, most of which were trained in the highly acrobatic Chinese opera and well versed with exotic martial arts weapons, this created a new spark for his use of bizarre weapons in his films. The Flag Of Iron is one of 20 movies that he directed featuring the utterly flabbergasting and physically exhausting action bits created by these five dudes. You have the good guys from the righteous clan versus the bad guys from the villainous clan and it's so filled with "don't-blink-or-you-will-miss-something" gags, you will need to watch it over and over again so you can see the things you missed.

programme.title: The Bride From Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: Accepted to the Golden Sword School after his father sacrificed his life to save his master, Fang Kang is resented by his fellow pupils and decides to leave. His master's daughter challenges him to a fight and cuts off his arm. Fang masters the art of sword fighting with one arm and finds himself returning to the School to save his master again.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them

programme.title: Till The End Of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: New Tales Of The Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandma's pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chief's daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth

programme.title: My Rebellious Son
programme.desc: A corrupt official attempts to steal a priceless Buddha statue from a temple to please a group of Westerners. Luckily, Doctor Zhang and his son manage to defeat the Western boxers, the Japanese Kendo opponents and the Western longsword fighters with Chinese kung fu, thus saving the Buddha statue.

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: Two Champions Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read and filmed novel in Chinese history, this version is said to be the most successful one. Betty Loh's looks, demeanour and aura in her portrayal of Lin Dai Yu has won her the epithet "Classic Beauty".

programme.title: The Hidden Power Of Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: Defeated villain Sung Ching Shu returns and starts a reign of terror, trapping a beautiful Mongolian Princess and mastering the "yin and yang combination" to become almost invincible. Only two swords held by two great swordsmen can stand in his way!

programme.title: Mr Funny - Bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Bao's chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keeper's daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: Mad Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Master Chen was an esteemed Monkey Kung Fu master, until he is framed and crippled by a ruthless villain and ends up becoming a wandering artiste. When Chen meets a young man, Little Monkey, on the streets, he decides to teach him all his monkey kung fu moves. Both men eventually team up to avenge Chen's past insult.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husband's playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: Lady Of The Law
programme.desc: Chan, the chief of Wan Sheng Escort, is forced to raise his opponent's son, Yim. While Chan forbids Yim to practice martial arts, Yim secretly learns it. Ten years later, a rapist appears and Yim is arrested by a lady constable as the suspect. The rapist turns out to be Chan's elder son and Yim is framed by the Chans. Can Yim prove his innocence?

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insider's look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiang's popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: The Black Tavern
programme.desc: This sword-filled thriller centres on The Black Tavern - an inn where the down and dirty meet to plot nefarious doings. A bunch of villains are lured to the inn by a rumour about a valuable treasure being hidden there. After all the backstabbing and killings, they realise that it is a trap created to wipe them out once and for all

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xu's until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: Legend Of The Fox
programme.desc: A young man, Chin, believes he is an orphan, until he meets three men and learns from them that his father was a great swordsman who was killed when he was trying to dispel rumors of a wrongdoing and return a lost sword to its rightful owner. Chin seeks out the men's help to take vengeance on the wrongful death of his father.

programme.title: The Emperor And The Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperor's plot once again.

programme.title: The Emperor And His Brother
programme.desc: The Emperor Qianlong is not the legitimate successor to the throne at birth, but he only learns the truth when two senior members of a subversive anti-government secret organisation contact him years later. As it happens, the chef of this organisation is Qianlong's younger brother and they must now confront each other in opposing roles

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards' heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: The Reckless Cricket
programme.desc: Inspired by Drunken Master, this kung fu comedy features a bumbling martial artist creating a cricket-style fighting arts to fight and defeat the different martial artists who have beaten him before.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: The movie consists of four stories of the Mad Monk helping others, from saving a mother and daughter from crumbling walls, to helping hawkers deal with bullies, recovering stolen money for a young man and punishing a devious court official and his son.

programme.title: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma S1 Ep89
programme.desc: The residents of Gokuldham Society encounter several adventures and misadventures as they navigate the ups and downs of life and overcome their struggles together in this animated series.

programme.title: Hagola S1 Ep8
programme.desc: HaGoLa' is the story of three naughty little friends - Lattha, Hathgola and Goli, who live in a unique world of objects.

programme.title: Hagola S1 Ep9
programme.desc: HaGoLa' is the story of three naughty little friends - Lattha, Hathgola and Goli, who live in a unique world of objects.

programme.title: Guru Aur Bhole S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Guru's onomatopoeic singing talents adds to Bhole's unique dancing style and brute strength which helps them to get out of many sticky situations in this animated musical comedy.

programme.title: Guru Aur Bhole S1 Ep16
programme.desc: Guru's onomatopoeic singing talents adds to Bhole's unique dancing style and brute strength which helps them to get out of many sticky situations in this animated musical comedy.

programme.title: Oh My Lallan S1 Ep22

programme.desc: Catch Me If You Sam / Toy Driver - Its Tag and Scoochs first day of Race Cadets and Sam Whippet tells the Cadets that whoever can catch him in a race will be the new team captain. \ When Mom donates a box of Tags old toys to the new daycare center, Tag decides that the only way to get her box of toys back is to go around town collecting toys to swap out for her toys.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back In The Crib Ep67
programme.desc: Inner Children - JJ reluctantly lets Tina take over her assistant duties for the day, but a Tina slip-up leads to an outbreak of town adults drinking diluted special formula that makes them all baby-brained. When JJ discovers this, she works with R & D Baby Simmons and Security Baby Katja to antidote the wobbling Adult Babies before Tina can find out and blame herself.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back In The Crib Ep68
programme.desc: Poompf! - Crispin Biscuits frames Boss and Tinas startup company for exploding baby Iggys favorite stuffed animal, and Tina is forced to the sidelines to avoid any more bad press. As Crispin expands his plan to burst all the plush toys in the neighborhood, Tina discovers she can stop this by breaking open and rewiring a single toy doll. Unfortunately that doll is Baby Corps current head honcho, Pull-String CEO Baby.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back In The Crib Ep69
programme.desc: The Heat is On - On the hottest week of the year and a miserable time for babies, Boss and Tim infiltrates a country club with a very cool splash pad in order to find some way around their strict no-babies policy. Meanwhile, Banker Baby Benny visits the startup company to check on his investment. Tina has to cover up how the heat has split her coworkers into lawless factions fighting over a fan and a mist cooler.

programme.title: The Epic Tales Of Captain Underpants Ep45
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Disturbing Dilemma Of The Dysfunctional Doppelgangers - The crew meets their blue-hued doppelgngers when they crash-land on an alien planet where kids call all the shots.

programme.title: The Croods Family Tree Ep7
programme.desc: Remote Control - Bored of the viewing options on window, Thunk realizes what hes been missing real life drama! But when Thunk starts creating drama around the farm, the others set out to teach him a lesson.

programme.title: The Croods Family Tree Ep8
programme.desc: Daddy Daughter Day - Sandy is finally old enough to join Grug and Eep for the annual Daddy Daughter Day and Grug couldnt be more excited. But when Sandy struggles to fit in with Grug and Eeps traditions, Grug has second thoughts. It isnt until Sandy goes missing that Grug realizes its time to start a new tradition.

programme.title: Abominable And The Invisible City Ep3
programme.desc: Sewer Koi and the Museum Heist - An earth-shaking rumble signals the arrival of a new creature, but Yi and Jin butt heads, each convinced theyre the better team leader. The crew eventually discovers that the massive Sewer Koi is behind the earthquakes, but hes missing his precious pearl, the key to a magical underground dam. Without it, the sewers water levels will rise, threatening to overflow and flood the whole city! Its going to take a heist to extract the pearl from its display at a local museum, before its too late.

programme.title: Abominable And The Invisible City Ep4
programme.desc: Peng vs. Peng - With the sudden closing of a local candy shop, NaiNai is busy trying to recreate its famous candied fruit. But after a late-night sugar binge in NaiNais stash, Peng starts acting strangely. It turns out that hes possessed by magical creatures! The Minticon are sugar-addicted puffball creatures, who previously lived in the old candy shop. Armed with her violin, Yi commands the creatures out of Pengs body, winning over the Minticon in the process.

programme.title: Abominable And The Invisible City Ep5
programme.desc: Jin's New Look - On the brink of his highly-anticipated White Coat Ceremony at school, Jin proudly dons his new white doctors coat around town, unwittingly drawing the attention of a creature named Morty. After a slobbery lick from Morty, Jin turns invisible! As Jin frantically tries to become re-visible, he discovers that Morty is very pregnant! Ultimately, Jin foregoes his ceremony and instead delivers Mortys five babies.

programme.title: Dragons 9 Realms Ep15
